room_title: Escape room "The Revolutionary" by Escape Room Lafayette in Lafayette
review: We had a great time! This was my second time there,  we had 7 players in the Fuggedaboutit room and we did awesome! We set the record on escaping and absolutely loved the room! Definitely plan on going back soon!

room_title: Escape room "The Revolutionary" by Escape Room Lafayette in Lafayette
review: Had a great time at this excellent team building activity. The staff was friendly and engaged. My team did the bar room and it was a little difficult but we did it. I could not have solved it by myself for sure. Everything about the experience was good!
